snippet: Ford Motor Co and its Chinese joint ventures sold 73,040 vehicles in China in February, up 67 percent from a year earlier, the U.S. automaker said on Thursday....

headline.print_headline: Ford Says February China Auto Sales Up 67 Percent Year/year
headline.main: Ford Says February China Auto Sales Up 67 Percent Year/year

lead_paragraph: Ford Motor Co and its Chinese joint ventures sold 73,040 vehicles in China in February, up 67 percent from a year earlier, the U.S. automaker said on Thursday.
